Hi amit

Ya my first phone interview was with him. He asked me mainly about my resume and a project i had done in the OS that i had taken. 
Then he asked me about multithreading in detail. He asked me about spinlocks and mutex, how to use them and how is spinlock implemented. 
Then he asked one algo questn to code. Given an integer and an index, flip the bit in the integer at that index. 

Hope this helps 😊

All the best (y)
